{"tid":604754,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"支持連登實名制 言論自由連登仔不配擁有","createTime":"2018-03-25T04:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T07:53:49.000Z","uid":47709,"like":38,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"748db85a590eaba81f7135cf9fccb6fd38d38fd0","tid":604754,"uid":47709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T04:54:43.000Z","msg":"連登真係好撚恐怖<br />\n好多人睇 同時會員質數極低<br />\n大量借刀 鳩up<br />\n是但post d相上黎就話人係雞<br />\n先唔好講無證無據<br />\n就算真係雞 唔明有咩討論價值<br />\n之前 vien都係咁<br />\n屌你老母 個時就開幾廿個post話人地雞<br />\n後尾又炒車 跟本重點唔係炒車 <br />\n而係一開始件事就唔撚關大家事啦<br />\n搞到人地工都無埋 而家賠翻份工比人？<br />\n<br />\n唔理係咪正確 每人都有自己嘅選擇 佢行嘅路<br />\n支持實名制 <br />\n睇下每個談論人地嘅人 到底現實生活入面點<br />\n以點樣嘅姿態公審人<br />\n幾咁醜陋<br />\n<br />\n屌人地雞個時就道德高地<br />\nJ人地流出個時就japjapjap<br />\n<br />\n言論自由？ 自由嘅背後 其實係一種自我約束<br />\n而唔係真係想講咩就講咩 做咩就做咩 <br />\n過火嘅時候就一句自由就大曬"},{"pid":"007b9959423c25f0af86225da1a97c8820847a75","tid":604754,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T07:50:03.000Z","msg":"質數極低<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06085a03f381baa9f5ab019a5f3eae30dda7a040","tid":604754,"uid":56721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T07:57:24.000Z","msg":"而家註冊同實名制沒分別"},{"pid":"d97408a174a84ef15a912e745f7584457f60bfdd","tid":604754,"uid":95,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T08:43:40.000Z","msg":"樓主五毛，正常人點會講得出實名制呢啲野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2aa5216f6afd05244e2c513b54eb68d097eaa5","tid":604754,"uid":3454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T08:45:33.000Z","msg":"睇完樓豬profile<br />\n樓豬怨氣好撚大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035a95a02cc2aca285188c662b44ee46f5edcf5a","tid":604754,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d97408a174a84ef15a912e745f7584457f60bfdd","tid":60